✨ Blush experiment in full swing! ✨ I tried Rose Pink on one side and Cherry Red Sun-Kissed on the other using the @charlottetilburyarabia Unreal Blush Sticks. They melt into the skin effortlessly, build like a dream, and leave the most gorgeous glow. 🌸🔥

Team Rose Pink 🌷🌸or Team Cherry Red?🍒?If you can’t decide… blend them together for your own custom shade! These blush sticks layer beautifully. 💖🍒
Amazing highlighter palette @forever52makeupofficial  Favorite brush set @jessupbeauty  multitasking amazing quality brushes 😍
